title: Aaron Rodgers Brilliantly Scrambles Out Of The Pocket For Nearly Nine Seconds And Throws Perfect Strike For TD
text:
Early in the season there was plenty of talk about Aaron Rodgers’demise but for the past few weeks the Packers QB has put most of that chatter to rest. 
In the fourth quarter of tonight’s Lions-Packers game, Rodgers brilliantly scrambled out of the pocket for nearly nine seconds before throwing a perfect strike of a touchdown pass.
Beast.
